WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.270
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.280 --> 00:00:05.190
Thank you for joining me today. Well, I've

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.990
had some things on my heart. I could go a

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.549
lot of different directions with this

00:00:09.559 --> 00:00:13.350
video. Diana and I

00:00:13.350 --> 00:00:13.360
both—she's

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:16.710
behind the camera

00:00:16.710 --> 00:00:16.720
today—had

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.310
an experience with the Holy Spirit.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.870
It was amazing the way He visited us.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:23.750
He

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:27.630
waited not on His day, but on Christmas,

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:27.640
because

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:29.310
we were celebrating. We had our

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:32.229
big party for Him, and we celebrated

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:34.790
the Lord as a family like we always

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:37.229
do. I felt the presence of the Lord

00:00:37.239 --> 00:00:39.190
very

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:41.389
strong. I sat on the

00:00:41.389 --> 00:00:41.399
couch—we

00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:43.950
were celebrating Christmas together—and it was

00:00:43.950 --> 00:00:43.960
close to midnight.

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:45.709
I was sitting on the couch

00:00:45.719 --> 00:00:49.189
and

00:00:56.359 --> 00:00:59.709
He said, 'Hey Brandon.'I said, 'Yes,

00:00:59.719 --> 00:01:00.630
Lord.'I

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:02.389
knew whenever He was about to talk.

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:04.710
I said, 'What's going on?'and He

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:07.190
said, 'It's almost Diana's birthday.

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:09.870
I want you to go and get her... I

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.070
want you to play a happy birthday song

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.550
and I want you to get ready. I want you

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.390
to celebrate her really big

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:17.830
for Me.'I said, 'For You, Lord?

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.990
I'll do it.'So I went and I got the

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.830
radio and I got the music so Stevie

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:26.390
Wonder could sing 'Happy

00:01:26.390 --> 00:01:26.400
Birthday.'At

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:28.350
the moment, because

00:01:28.350 --> 00:01:28.360
I had

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:30.789
lost track of time, the

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:33.670
Holy Spirit wanted it to be special

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:38.149
at the exact second. So

00:01:38.159 --> 00:01:40.230
I turned the music on, got it all going,

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:43.350
and we all did our little dance

00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:46.590
and celebrated and had fun with the kids

00:01:46.590 --> 00:01:46.600
because

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:48.190
it was Diana's birthday. Now He said,

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.149
'Sit down, I have something to

00:01:50.149 --> 00:01:50.159
say.'I

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:54.550
was like,

00:01:54.550 --> 00:01:54.560
'Whoa.'The

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:57.310
prophetic anointing went like a blanket

00:01:57.320 --> 00:01:58.830
in our

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:01.149
house, and the presence of the Lord

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:04.429
filled our home. He said, 'I waited to

00:02:04.439 --> 00:02:08.070
speak not on My day, but on your day,'for He always deflects. He

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:11.190
said, 'Brandon...'it was the way He said

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:13.949
it.

00:02:13.959 --> 00:02:17.589
Diana, do you remember

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:20.150
exactly the words He used? Yeah, the Holy

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:23.509
Spirit said, 'I always deflect the

00:02:23.519 --> 00:02:27.670
glory upwards to Heaven, towards Jesus

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:30.550
and the Father.'He said,

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:33.030
'You've always

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:35.470
asked these questions of Me,

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:37.589
and you've never

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:40.589
had the answer. Today, I'm

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:43.630
going to answer some questions about

00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:43.640
Me.'Ladies

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:47.309
and

00:02:47.319 --> 00:02:51.949
gentlemen, in visions, He appeared before

00:02:51.959 --> 00:02:56.350
me. To

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:59.149
describe what the Holy Spirit would look

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:00.630
like in the

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:04.309
natural, I can't. It is

00:03:05.319 --> 00:03:10.670
breathtaking.

00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:13.390
I had a

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:16.509
visitation. I've had a lot of amazing

00:03:16.519 --> 00:03:19.149
things that the Lord over the years

00:03:19.149 --> 00:03:19.159
has

00:03:19.159 --> 00:03:20.750
showed

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:24.030
me, but this was beyond one of the top

00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:28.270
experiences I've ever had.

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:31.390
As He

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:33.990
came, whenever He was talking about the

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.470
giftings being poured out on the

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:41.429
25th, He

00:03:41.439 --> 00:03:44.630
showed me the Chariots of Fire

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:48.470
flowing over the Earth's

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:51.030
atmosphere. I saw the gifts being

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:53.670
distributed out to the people,

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:55.229
floating down and going

00:03:55.239 --> 00:03:58.030
inside of them as the Chariots of Fire

00:03:58.040 --> 00:04:00.030
were going around, similar to what you

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:03.390
would consider Santa's sleigh, but it

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:06.830
was angelic. All of them were distributing,

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:09.630
floating above the atmosphere of the

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:11.910
Earth, and I could see them shooting

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:13.710
around, giving the gifts

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:16.150
out to the people—the spiritual

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:19.990
mantles. Whenever they did, it floated

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.629
down and went inside of them as

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:24.950
impartations. This is what I saw in the

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:28.390
visions. The Lord showed me certain

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:31.110
boxes and said to me,

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:33.629
'You see those boxes? I wanted to

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:35.590
bring the gift, but they weren't ready

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:38.670
for it.'Because they weren't ready for it,

00:04:38.670 --> 00:04:38.680
He

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:40.670
had

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:43.430
to take it back. There were not

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:46.830
as many gifts distributed

00:04:46.830 --> 00:04:46.840
as

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:49.110
was originally planned

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:50.710
because the people's hearts weren't

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.110
ready. They had a hardened heart.

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:55.189
He can only

00:04:55.199 --> 00:04:57.270
bring what you will

00:04:57.280 --> 00:05:00.629
receive;

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:03.430
the Holy Spirit is a gentleman

00:05:03.430 --> 00:05:03.440
who

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:07.790
loves His children, but if you reject Him

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:10.790
and say, 'I don't want

00:05:10.790 --> 00:05:10.800
that,'He

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:12.670
can't give you something that you don't

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:16.070
want. So whenever He said to me those

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:18.270
people were not ready to receive it, it

00:05:18.270 --> 00:05:18.280
was because

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:20.670
they wanted more of the

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:23.230
world than they wanted Him. They

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:26.189
wanted more of what their

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:28.550
flesh desired than to crucify their

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.469
flesh and pick up the cross and

00:05:30.479 --> 00:05:31.510
follow

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:35.590
Him. I felt so grieved as I saw the

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:38.150
Chariot of Fire turn and go back up into

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.309
heaven, and they had that package still

00:05:40.319 --> 00:05:42.710
on the back of that chariot.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.909
He was ready; He wanted to give

00:05:44.919 --> 00:05:47.390
it, but their heart was hardened towards it

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:49.270
and they didn't want

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:52.790
it. But the gifts were delivered on

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:55.189
Christmas, just like He said they would. I

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:57.390
saw them, and they fell down and

00:05:57.400 --> 00:06:00.350
went into the people.

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:02.870
They were beautiful gifts, and He

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:06.790
said, 'These are end-time

00:06:06.790 --> 00:06:06.800
mantles

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:09.430
that the glorious church will

00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:13.430
walk in now.'He says as of this day

00:06:13.440 --> 00:06:15.670
things will change, and you will see it

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:18.110
now. In a 24-hour period, you'll start to

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:20.950
see the development—cultivation is a

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:23.270
good word—of it coming

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:26.430
up out of you as you keep your eyes

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:29.589
vertical towards Me, always looking up

00:06:29.599 --> 00:06:31.670
towards Me, not

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:34.790
horizontal. Keeping it

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:37.830
vertical is what's going to change you

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:40.189
in the days ahead, keeping in step with

00:06:40.199 --> 00:06:43.870
Me.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:43.880
And

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:47.550
the Holy

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:50.189
Spirit showed me a massive,

00:06:50.199 --> 00:06:55.950
beautiful glove that represented

00:06:55.960 --> 00:07:00.070
us. He showed me Him, and He was a

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:03.150
hand; He went into the glove and

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:06.110
empowered it. But the glove was

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:08.990
lifeless without Him; it flopped around

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:11.629
like a leather glove would without the

00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:13.830
Holy Spirit. As the Holy Spirit

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:15.589
filled that

00:07:15.599 --> 00:07:18.430
glove, the glove became alive, and He was

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:21.150
able to use it. The

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:23.150
glove touches things, the glove lifts

00:07:23.160 --> 00:07:25.790
things, the hand

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:29.309
removes things, but it's the Holy Spirit

00:07:29.319 --> 00:07:32.230
in the glove. A human hand is

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:34.309
what gives the glove power. Does that

00:07:34.319 --> 00:07:36.830
make sense? So the Holy

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:39.629
Spirit came in that glove, and the glove

00:07:39.639 --> 00:07:43.550
started to glow. As long as the

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:46.350
hand was

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:48.950
inside that glove, it had power.

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:51.830
Whenever He took His hand out of it, the

00:07:51.840 --> 00:07:54.510
glove was lifeless

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:57.149
again. So He showed

00:07:57.159 --> 00:08:01.710
me what His mission is always to do.

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:04.350
I saw a massive

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:07.990
mirror. He was holding the mirror, and

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.869
He seems really mysterious

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:11.710
to the natural mind because He's

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.430
real quiet and to Himself.

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:15.869
Whenever you feel His presence,

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:18.589
it changes everything, but

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:20.670
it's always to give God the glory,

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:22.469
to give the Father glory and

00:08:22.479 --> 00:08:25.869
Jesus the glory. Holy Spirit was taking

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:29.149
us and all the praise that was coming

00:08:29.159 --> 00:08:31.710
from the Body of Christ. 'Holy Spirit,

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:34.670
Thou art welcome in this

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:37.269
place.'He

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:40.070
was taking that

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:42.070
mirror and shining it

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:44.110
towards

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:45.949
the

00:08:45.959 --> 00:08:49.190
Father. Just like Jesus says, 'I do

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.430
nothing in this earth without my Father

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:54.430
instructing me to do it, and I give all

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:57.350
the glory to the

00:08:57.350 --> 00:08:57.360
Father.'Jesus

00:08:57.360 --> 00:09:00.389
was the Lord in the flesh; the

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:03.030
Word became flesh and dwelt among us, the

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:06.190
Bible says. The Holy Spirit was always

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:10.310
magnifying with that mirror, shining that

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:13.509
light and reflecting it on the

00:09:13.519 --> 00:09:16.389
Father. Every single

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:18.790
time praise was coming

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:22.269
towards Him,

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:25.990
He said, 'I always keep

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:28.990
myself humble before the

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:30.150
Father.'The

00:09:30.160 --> 00:09:33.350
Spirit was keeping humble before the

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:36.590
Father by pushing the praises to the

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:38.790
Father. There are

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:41.710
three: Jesus, the Father, and the Holy

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:44.310
Spirit. And the way He

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:50.509
appeared to me

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:53.829
was glorious. I will not go into

00:09:53.839 --> 00:09:57.389
the way He looked;

00:09:57.389 --> 00:09:57.399
there

00:09:57.399 --> 00:10:00.550
are

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:02.430
no

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:05.430
words in the English vocabulary that can

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:08.030
go into the depth and try to

00:10:08.040 --> 00:10:10.870
explain. He's vast; He had a

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.790
barrel chest. I saw Him

00:10:13.790 --> 00:10:13.800
in

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.110
physical

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:19.790
form. He formed Himself before me, and I

00:10:19.800 --> 00:10:23.470
could see His robe.

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:25.990
I can honestly tell you,

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:28.470
it was beyond anything

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.630
my natural mind can

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:33.509
comprehend. He showed me,

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:35.910
'Brandon, I will work with you now, and

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:38.990
we will work together at a greater

00:10:38.990 --> 00:10:39.000
level—you,

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:42.389
your wife, and your

00:10:42.389 --> 00:10:42.399
son—for

00:10:42.399 --> 00:10:44.949
this ministry that I'm calling you

00:10:44.949 --> 00:10:44.959
to.'He

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:48.910
says, 'As you walk this

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:52.590
out, we will work well together as long

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:55.949
as you realize that you are a man and

00:10:55.959 --> 00:11:00.710
you will deflect the praise from

00:11:00.710 --> 00:11:00.720
men

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:02.629
that will try to be given to you because

00:11:02.639 --> 00:11:04.150
of the anointing that you will walk

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:07.310
under. You will always deflect the glory

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.230
to the

00:11:08.230 --> 00:11:08.240
Father.'He

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:11.269
said as long as you always

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:14.629
deflect the glory to the Father, we will

00:11:14.639 --> 00:11:17.829
get along just fine. But the moment you

00:11:17.839 --> 00:11:20.629
ever take the praise for

00:11:20.639 --> 00:11:24.710
yourself, it's

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:28.389
done. That's how serious it

00:11:28.399 --> 00:11:31.509
was. 'You are a

00:11:31.519 --> 00:11:33.790
man,

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:38.710
and you are always to deflect the

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:41.870
glory from yourself and be quick

00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:44.949
to give the Father the glory and praise

00:11:44.959 --> 00:11:47.710
for what He's doing through you. You are

00:11:47.720 --> 00:11:48.470
a

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:52.269
glove that I will operate through,

00:11:52.279 --> 00:11:54.550
but our job is to always deflect the

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:56.990
glory to the Father and to

00:11:56.990 --> 00:11:57.000
Jesus.'Does

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:58.910
this make sense,

00:11:58.920 --> 00:12:02.590
folks? It was so out there.

00:12:02.600 --> 00:12:05.310
He said, 'As of today, you will operate

00:12:05.320 --> 00:12:08.509
with the angels, and your ministry will

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:11.670
grow in a greater capacity in

00:12:11.680 --> 00:12:13.150
healing and demonstrations and

00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:15.350
manifestations of this great outpouring

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.670
that I'm about to do in this

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:20.189
earth.'He

00:12:20.199 --> 00:12:22.550
spoke to me and showed me the

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:24.470
angels, and they were standing at

00:12:24.480 --> 00:12:26.710
attention. He said, 'You will work with

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:28.269
them, but you're not to communicate with

00:12:28.279 --> 00:12:31.110
them on a one-on-one basis like this; it's

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:33.430
through

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.189
Me.'I

00:12:35.199 --> 00:12:36.710
won't go into depth of

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:41.110
all that, but it was a

00:12:41.110 --> 00:12:41.120
'wow'as

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:43.629
the angel hosts were standing before me.

00:12:43.639 --> 00:12:45.790
The Lord said, 'This is how you

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:47.470
will do this

00:12:47.470 --> 00:12:47.480
together.'He

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:49.670
commissioned me and showed me all of

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:51.949
this. He

00:12:51.949 --> 00:12:51.959
started

00:12:51.959 --> 00:12:55.389
talking to me about Diana and said

00:12:55.399 --> 00:12:58.310
great things about my wife,

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.870
beautiful things.

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:01.509
If she ever wants to tell you those

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:03.189
things, she can,

00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:06.750
but some of it is private.

00:13:06.760 --> 00:13:08.269
Then He spoke to me about my

00:13:08.279 --> 00:13:10.629
children.

00:13:10.639 --> 00:13:13.910
After this visitation that

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.910
lasted for

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:18.269
probably 45 minutes

00:13:18.269 --> 00:13:18.279
to

00:13:18.279 --> 00:13:20.030
an hour,

00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:27.069
it was

00:13:27.079 --> 00:13:32.670
so

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:36.829
holy. It was a Holy

00:13:36.839 --> 00:13:40.350
Experience. 'Holy, holy, holy is

00:13:40.360 --> 00:13:43.310
the Lord of hosts.'And who am I that the

00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:45.870
Father would want to visit

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:48.670
me, my wife, and my children on

00:13:48.680 --> 00:13:52.069
her birthday? It was such an honor.

00:13:52.079 --> 00:13:55.629
As my wife wept, we all wept that

00:13:55.639 --> 00:13:58.030
He would wait until her birthday, until

00:13:58.040 --> 00:14:00.550
the clock struck

00:14:00.560 --> 00:14:04.110
midnight, to

00:14:04.110 --> 00:14:04.120
say,

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:07.710
'Now I want to celebrate

00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:10.470
you; I want to celebrate your

00:14:10.470 --> 00:14:10.480
life.'He

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:12.389
gave my wife a

00:14:12.399 --> 00:14:15.870
vision of her being birthed,

00:14:18.399 --> 00:14:21.189
how He breathed the first breath she ever

00:14:21.199 --> 00:14:24.269
took. She saw herself in that,

00:14:24.279 --> 00:14:28.470
as a baby taking

00:14:28.470 --> 00:14:28.480
her

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:29.629
first breath,

00:14:29.639 --> 00:14:33.710
and the Holy Spirit breathed life into

00:14:33.720 --> 00:14:36.389
her.

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:39.069
God said, 'I was there.

00:14:39.079 --> 00:14:41.150
I'm a proud father

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:45.150
today.'She

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:49.269
could see the

00:14:49.279 --> 00:14:52.150
nurses taking care of her,

00:14:54.959 --> 00:14:57.150
cleaning her up as she was

00:14:57.160 --> 00:15:04.230
being brought into this

00:15:04.240 --> 00:15:07.389
world. I tell you these things that are

00:15:07.399 --> 00:15:11.550
so precious to

00:15:11.560 --> 00:15:15.189
us not to brag, but to fan your flame

00:15:15.199 --> 00:15:17.110
because there's more out

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:20.749
there. I came in the last

00:15:20.759 --> 00:15:24.269
video and it hurt a lot; a lot of the

00:15:24.279 --> 00:15:26.069
comments and persecution hurt.

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:30.670
My heart is always to help

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:34.230
you and to pour

00:15:34.240 --> 00:15:37.069
out everything I have because I know

00:15:37.079 --> 00:15:38.910
you're hurting so bad. But there's some of

00:15:38.910 --> 00:15:38.920
you—it's

00:15:38.920 --> 00:15:40.629
like a

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:42.990
dog that's been hit in the

00:15:43.000 --> 00:15:45.990
street. You go out there to help the dog

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:47.749
that's been injured,

00:15:47.759 --> 00:15:50.670
and the natural reaction, because

00:15:50.680 --> 00:15:53.829
that dog is in pain,

00:15:53.839 --> 00:15:56.870
is

00:15:56.880 --> 00:15:59.470
that the dog retaliates

00:15:59.480 --> 00:16:02.069
and bites the hand of the one trying to

00:16:02.079 --> 00:16:03.550
help

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:07.389
him. I feel there's a lot of you that

00:16:07.399 --> 00:16:10.990
have a lot of pain, and as I reach down

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:13.150
to try to pick you up out of the gutter

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:14.590
that you've been thrown

00:16:14.600 --> 00:16:20.550
in by life's trauma, abuse,

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:20.560
and

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:23.829
rejection, you have a tendency to try to

00:16:23.839 --> 00:16:26.389
bite the hand that's trying to help you.

00:16:26.399 --> 00:16:29.309
My heart is pure. I just want to

00:16:29.319 --> 00:16:32.030
lift you up and tell you that Jesus has

00:16:32.040 --> 00:16:34.550
a plan for your life, and that's not

00:16:34.560 --> 00:16:36.509
always received well from some of

00:16:36.519 --> 00:16:38.749
you because I see your emails

00:16:38.749 --> 00:16:38.759
and

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:40.910
comments. My son had to spend half his

00:16:40.920 --> 00:16:44.749
day erasing the comments from the people

00:16:44.759 --> 00:16:46.710
biting

00:16:46.720 --> 00:16:50.629
us. You call me a false prophet, you call

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:54.509
me all these terrible things.

00:16:57.319 --> 00:17:00.350
I'm

00:17:00.360 --> 00:17:03.110
not here to make you feel sorry for me; I

00:17:03.120 --> 00:17:05.510
just see you as you're hurting, and we're

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:08.350
here to help you.

00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:14.069
I watched as it grieved me when I

00:17:14.079 --> 00:17:16.990
made the communion first, showing you the

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.829
birthday cake, giving God praise first,

00:17:19.839 --> 00:17:21.870
and then giving you what my heart was

00:17:21.880 --> 00:17:24.429
pure to give you as a Christmas present. You

00:17:24.429 --> 00:17:24.439
fast-forwarded

00:17:24.439 --> 00:17:26.909
all that, and the

00:17:26.919 --> 00:17:28.990
algorithm shows me you didn't want

00:17:28.990 --> 00:17:29.000
anything

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:31.350
to do with Jesus.

00:17:31.360 --> 00:17:36.190
Almost 55% out of

00:17:36.190 --> 00:17:36.200
70,000

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:39.990
views had nothing to

00:17:40.000 --> 00:17:42.990
do with communion, nothing to do with

00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:44.909
giving God

00:17:44.919 --> 00:17:48.870
glory. You just wanted what would benefit

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:52.590
you; you just wanted what would make you

00:17:52.600 --> 00:17:54.390
rich

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:58.230
potentially. We're

00:17:58.240 --> 00:18:00.390
all human and we

00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:02.990
see through the glass dimly or

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.669
darkly,

00:18:05.679 --> 00:18:08.870
but you don't want a relationship

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:09.830
with

00:18:09.840 --> 00:18:14.630
Him. He wants a relationship with you so

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:18.390
bad. He looks for it every day, but you

00:18:18.400 --> 00:18:23.270
don't even

00:18:40.240 --> 00:18:43.110
want to give Him

00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:46.350
value for His birthday. You say it's

00:18:46.360 --> 00:18:48.630
not His birthday, it's just the day that we

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:50.750
celebrate

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:53.310
it.

00:18:53.320 --> 00:18:56.590
Well,

00:18:56.600 --> 00:18:59.310
if you pick a day,

00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:04.750
at

00:19:04.760 --> 00:19:07.510
least celebrate Him. If you don't want to

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:09.390
celebrate December 25th because you say it's a

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:11.149
pagan holiday and I get

00:19:11.149 --> 00:19:11.159
ridiculed

00:19:11.159 --> 00:19:15.029
for it, then by all means, pick December

00:19:15.039 --> 00:19:19.149
27th. I don't care. But

00:19:19.159 --> 00:19:21.510
He came as a man, died,

00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:23.630
and rose again for you so that you don't

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:26.110
have to go to hell. He

00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:35.270
deserves our praise and our

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:38.470
worship regardless.

00:19:38.470 --> 00:19:38.480
Fast-forwarding

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:42.029
it

00:19:42.039 --> 00:19:44.470
all just to get what He

00:19:44.480 --> 00:19:45.630
gives so

00:19:45.640 --> 00:19:48.149
freely... He said, 'I come that you might

00:19:48.159 --> 00:19:51.230
have life and life more

00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:51.240
abundantly.'What

00:19:51.240 --> 00:19:54.190
does that mean to you?

00:19:56.640 --> 00:19:59.789
He wants for you

00:19:59.789 --> 00:19:59.799
to

00:19:59.799 --> 00:20:01.549
have life and life

00:20:01.559 --> 00:20:04.310
more abundantly, to the full until it

00:20:04.320 --> 00:20:07.390
overflows. He said, 'Beloved, I wish above all

00:20:07.400 --> 00:20:10.830
things that you prosper and be in health,

00:20:10.840 --> 00:20:14.230
even as your soul

00:20:14.230 --> 00:20:14.240
prospers.'Everything

00:20:14.240 --> 00:20:18.110
that you ever need,

00:20:18.120 --> 00:20:20.549
He's already provided,

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:28.909
but you want to bypass intimacy.

00:20:30.360 --> 00:20:34.710
53% want to bypass the intimacy of the

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:38.470
Father to get to the blessing

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:42.070
only, and that's treating Him like a

00:20:42.070 --> 00:20:42.080
whore,

00:20:42.080 --> 00:20:46.270
and it grieved me.

00:20:46.280 --> 00:20:48.830
So I give you something that's so

00:20:48.840 --> 00:20:50.870
precious to me and you say, 'Well, Brandon,

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:53.029
you're a false prophet. You said a crash

00:20:53.039 --> 00:20:55.750
was

00:20:55.750 --> 00:20:55.760
coming.'I

00:20:55.760 --> 00:20:58.669
told you, ladies and gentlemen, He said He

00:20:58.679 --> 00:21:01.149
wanted to give us a window of

00:21:01.159 --> 00:21:03.630
opportunity. He said, 'I will not hold

00:21:03.640 --> 00:21:05.070
anything from My

00:21:05.070 --> 00:21:05.080
beloved.'He

00:21:05.080 --> 00:21:08.990
came to Abraham and warned

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:11.230
him what was coming in Sodom and

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:15.950
Gomorrah to help Lot. So, as His

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:23.190
friend, He comes and warns His friends

00:21:23.200 --> 00:21:24.310
what's

00:21:24.320 --> 00:21:27.430
coming and says, 'I want to give My

00:21:27.440 --> 00:21:30.750
friends more time. I want to give them a

00:21:30.760 --> 00:21:33.510
window because what's coming will

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:37.510
devastate many of

00:21:37.510 --> 00:21:37.520
you.'A

00:21:37.520 --> 00:21:40.070
lot of you will not make it out

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:40.080
of—is

00:21:40.080 --> 00:21:43.590
it a tribulation? It's the birthing

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:46.470
pains before tribulation. You do not have

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:48.510
a comprehension of how bad

00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:52.549
tribulation will be, but He is giving a

00:21:52.559 --> 00:21:55.070
window of opportunity before the ark

00:21:55.080 --> 00:21:56.070
door

00:21:56.080 --> 00:21:59.070
closes. He wants you to be

00:21:59.080 --> 00:22:02.470
prepared, so He speaks through me and you

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:05.549
take what is holy at the

00:22:05.559 --> 00:22:08.750
beginning and rub your feet all over it.

00:22:08.750 --> 00:22:08.760
You

00:22:08.760 --> 00:22:10.870
just grab ahold of what

00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:13.070
you thought would benefit

00:22:13.080 --> 00:22:17.110
you, but you're missing it. He is what

00:22:17.120 --> 00:22:18.750
will benefit

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:21.909
you. This is all going to burn.

00:22:21.919 --> 00:22:26.350
Money is a tool to

00:22:26.360 --> 00:22:28.710
bring forth the glory

00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:38.029
for

00:22:38.039 --> 00:22:41.230
Him. The very thing that you think that

00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:43.909
you don't need at the beginning is what

00:22:43.919 --> 00:22:46.590
would change you, so it's to sustain you for

00:22:46.600 --> 00:22:49.990
this, but this is just a tool. And the

00:22:49.990 --> 00:22:50.000
world—that's

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:52.230
all they

00:22:52.240 --> 00:22:54.630
want, but yet they're so empty. They're

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:56.549
the dog in the road biting

00:22:56.549 --> 00:22:56.559
the

00:22:56.559 --> 00:22:58.710
people's hands,

00:22:58.720 --> 00:23:02.110
trying to figure out how to fill the

00:23:02.120 --> 00:23:05.630
hurt. All the busted and disgusted

00:23:05.640 --> 00:23:09.230
memories... you bite the hand wanting

00:23:09.240 --> 00:23:11.669
what you think you need, and you have no

00:23:11.679 --> 00:23:14.110
idea what you need. You need

00:23:14.120 --> 00:23:17.269
Him. You need communion; you need

00:23:17.279 --> 00:23:21.230
fellowship. To the

00:23:21.230 --> 00:23:21.240
20-some percent

00:23:21.240 --> 00:23:24.430
of you that wanted it,

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:29.669
I pray it blessed

00:23:29.679 --> 00:23:33.430
you. This is what will cause

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:36.669
you to grow up spiritually and hear Him.

00:23:36.679 --> 00:23:39.390
'I will hear the Lord's voice, and

00:23:39.400 --> 00:23:42.430
a stranger's voice I will not

00:23:42.430 --> 00:23:42.440
follow.'This

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:45.750
is what you need to hear Him,

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:48.269
because if you spend time here,

00:23:48.279 --> 00:23:53.350
you'll hear for this. But this is so

00:23:53.350 --> 00:23:53.360
volatile;

00:23:53.360 --> 00:23:57.190
it goes up and down so much.

00:23:59.400 --> 00:24:01.070
You think you're going to maintain and

00:24:01.080 --> 00:24:04.390
keep it? You won't. He said if you're not

00:24:04.400 --> 00:24:06.630
hearing Me and

00:24:06.640 --> 00:24:08.710
being vertical,

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:11.590
you will not know when to pull

00:24:11.600 --> 00:24:14.190
your money out, and you will not know

00:24:14.200 --> 00:24:16.149
when to put your money

00:24:16.159 --> 00:24:20.070
in. He told me that many,

00:24:20.080 --> 00:24:22.510
because all they want is this, will

00:24:22.520 --> 00:24:25.830
be broke in a 24-hour period. They will

00:24:25.840 --> 00:24:28.789
lose it all. They don't even realize

00:24:28.799 --> 00:24:30.470
they've been brought to the

00:24:30.480 --> 00:24:32.750
starting line, but they'll never make it

00:24:32.760 --> 00:24:36.590
to the finish line

00:24:36.600 --> 00:24:38.950
because you do not

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:42.430
realize how bad it's about to

00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:46.070
get. He gave us a window and called

00:24:46.080 --> 00:24:49.669
this a season of grace. How

00:24:49.669 --> 00:24:49.679
long is

00:24:49.679 --> 00:24:51.470
that season? I

00:24:51.480 --> 00:24:53.630
don't know. When you're looking into a

00:24:53.640 --> 00:24:55.190
vision, you think it's four years, but it

00:24:55.200 --> 00:24:56.909
could be four days, four

00:24:56.919 --> 00:24:58.590
weeks, four months, or

00:24:58.590 --> 00:24:58.600
forty

00:24:58.600 --> 00:25:02.870
years. All I know is

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:06.950
the season that is coming is very dark

00:25:06.960 --> 00:25:10.430
for the world, and great financial

00:25:10.440 --> 00:25:12.710
hardship is

00:25:12.720 --> 00:25:17.669
coming. Dark days, so much so that

00:25:17.679 --> 00:25:19.510
many of you will stand in

00:25:19.520 --> 00:25:23.549
line for hours

00:25:23.549 --> 00:25:23.559
just

00:25:23.559 --> 00:25:25.990
to get

00:25:26.000 --> 00:25:27.110
a

00:25:28.110 --> 00:25:28.120
bag—I

00:25:31.399 --> 00:25:33.350
saw a

00:25:33.360 --> 00:25:35.909
grocery sack of food, a paper sack of

00:25:35.919 --> 00:25:39.669
food that they'll give you by FEMA

00:25:39.679 --> 00:25:42.870
because there are great trade wars with

00:25:42.880 --> 00:25:47.430
China and America coming. We

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:51.269
depend solely on China for a lot of our

00:25:51.279 --> 00:25:54.149
goods, and when the tariffs come in,

00:25:54.159 --> 00:25:56.990
remember what I tell you: there will be a

00:25:57.000 --> 00:25:59.909
day when China says, 'We're not sending

00:25:59.919 --> 00:26:01.950
anything; we're not doing business with

00:26:01.960 --> 00:26:04.549
you for a while'as a

00:26:04.559 --> 00:26:08.310
strike. When this strike takes place,

00:26:08.320 --> 00:26:10.630
our grocery stores, our Walmarts, our

00:26:10.640 --> 00:26:14.310
Targets will have nothing in them. I saw

00:26:14.320 --> 00:26:17.070
shelves with cobwebs in the corners,

00:26:17.080 --> 00:26:20.070
representing a longer period of

00:26:20.080 --> 00:26:22.510
time with nothing on

00:26:22.520 --> 00:26:25.230
them. They had to take the goods from

00:26:25.240 --> 00:26:27.750
one store and put it in another to

00:26:27.760 --> 00:26:30.149
fill that store up,

00:26:31.559 --> 00:26:33.590
then

00:26:35.080 --> 00:26:37.470
shut that store

00:26:37.480 --> 00:26:39.669
down. That's how bad it

00:26:39.679 --> 00:26:44.630
was. I saw a house of cards

00:26:44.640 --> 00:26:47.029
falling. I saw interest rates

00:26:47.039 --> 00:26:49.350
skyrocketing again because they couldn't

00:26:49.360 --> 00:26:52.669
control it. Everything they are trying to

00:26:52.679 --> 00:26:55.990
tell you right now with Jerome Powell and

00:26:56.000 --> 00:26:59.310
all that—they don't know what to do.

00:26:59.320 --> 00:27:01.110
The house of cards is

00:27:01.120 --> 00:27:04.510
falling, folks. We see that Donald

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:06.789
Trump will come in with a plan

00:27:06.799 --> 00:27:09.110
orchestrated by the Solomon

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:10.549
anointing that God's going to use him

00:27:10.559 --> 00:27:14.230
for, but I saw a

00:27:14.240 --> 00:27:16.430
period of darkness. He took the

00:27:16.440 --> 00:27:18.789
paddles and he brought America back, and

00:27:18.799 --> 00:27:20.750
the darkness lifted a little bit.

00:27:24.440 --> 00:27:26.710
The shock came and it

00:27:26.720 --> 00:27:28.710
lifted the darkness up above the trees

00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:30.830
so that we can maintain life a little

00:27:30.840 --> 00:27:34.549
bit, that America could have a reprieve.

00:27:34.559 --> 00:27:37.470
Because what is coming is a dam of bad

00:27:37.480 --> 00:27:39.830
things that has tried to manifest on

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:43.310
America because of the past

00:27:43.320 --> 00:27:45.590
administration.

00:27:45.600 --> 00:27:48.430
It is by the grace of

00:27:48.440 --> 00:27:50.549
God if this thing does not all fall

00:27:50.559 --> 00:27:53.950
apart.

00:27:56.120 --> 00:27:58.750
I saw

00:27:58.750 --> 00:27:58.760
churches

00:27:58.760 --> 00:28:00.590
and major congregations close

00:28:00.590 --> 00:28:00.600
down

00:28:00.600 --> 00:28:01.789
because the notes on their churches

00:28:01.789 --> 00:28:01.799
were

00:28:01.799 --> 00:28:03.350
too much;

00:28:03.360 --> 00:28:04.710
the people

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:06.190
weren't able to give to help support

00:28:06.200 --> 00:28:10.230
these

00:28:10.230 --> 00:28:10.240
megachurches.

00:28:10.240 --> 00:28:13.310
But God told me that He would

00:28:13.320 --> 00:28:16.909
protect His remnant. I

00:28:16.919 --> 00:28:19.789
pray you're one of them—the ones

00:28:19.799 --> 00:28:21.310
that want to take

00:28:21.320 --> 00:28:24.149
communion, the ones that look

00:28:24.159 --> 00:28:27.070
to Him and are desperate. They are

00:28:27.080 --> 00:28:29.310
