00:49:23.319 --> 00:49:25.230
visits you on your wife's

00:49:25.240 --> 00:49:27.230
birthday and the presence of the Lord

00:49:27.240 --> 00:49:28.710
fills your whole house, and

00:49:34.400 --> 00:49:37.270
He allows you to see something

00:49:37.280 --> 00:49:40.309
so holy.

00:50:13.200 --> 00:50:17.829
God, help

00:50:17.839 --> 00:50:22.030
me.

00:50:30.400 --> 00:50:41.309
I pray that you would know

00:50:41.309 --> 00:50:41.319
Him—not

00:50:41.319 --> 00:50:44.069
about

00:50:44.079 --> 00:50:47.510
Him.

00:50:47.520 --> 00:50:49.069
You can know a lot about me, but you

00:50:49.079 --> 00:50:51.950
don't know me.

00:50:59.920 --> 00:51:01.670
You spend your life with the one

00:51:01.680 --> 00:51:03.870
you love the most and you become

00:51:03.880 --> 00:51:06.470
intimate with them.

00:51:33.839 --> 00:51:37.430
My desire today is for you to

00:51:37.440 --> 00:51:38.349
know

00:51:38.359 --> 00:51:44.069
Him.

00:51:46.160 --> 00:51:48.950
I'm going to do my best to come on

00:51:48.960 --> 00:51:50.470
as much as the Holy Spirit will give me

00:51:50.480 --> 00:51:53.309
a word, but I am not coming on here

00:51:53.319 --> 00:51:56.150
every day if I don't have a

00:51:56.160 --> 00:51:57.750
word.

00:52:03.040 --> 00:52:05.710
This is His

00:52:05.720 --> 00:52:09.390
channel, and if I don't feel

00:52:09.400 --> 00:52:12.190
that He's inside the

00:52:12.200 --> 00:52:14.549
glove, I am not going to operate.

00:52:59.400 --> 00:53:01.910
I'm not a

00:53:01.920 --> 00:53:04.789
content creator; I am a person who wants

00:53:04.799 --> 00:53:07.670
to bring a fresh breath

00:53:07.670 --> 00:53:07.680
of

00:53:07.680 --> 00:53:10.270
living water to you.

00:53:25.440 --> 00:53:29.710
We love you all. Father,

00:53:29.720 --> 00:53:31.270
I pray for every single one of them

00:53:31.280 --> 00:53:34.069
today. I thank You for that fresh

00:53:34.079 --> 00:53:36.789
touch and that fresh drink of

00:53:36.799 --> 00:53:39.270
Your living water. I thank You,

00:53:41.200 --> 00:53:43.990
Father,

00:53:44.000 --> 00:53:46.150
that there is a supernatural outpouring

00:53:46.160 --> 00:53:49.349
of Your Spirit.

00:54:00.920 --> 00:54:03.190
I thank You, Lord, that we're

00:54:03.200 --> 00:54:05.270
always at the right place at the right

00:54:05.280 --> 00:54:07.789
time, hearing Your voice.

00:54:18.880 --> 00:54:21.470
I

00:54:21.480 --> 00:54:23.430
thank You for every single person

00:54:23.440 --> 00:54:25.309
represented here today—that they're

00:54:25.319 --> 00:54:27.470
blessed and prosperous, and their

00:54:27.480 --> 00:54:29.870
minds are renewed. I

00:54:29.870 --> 00:54:29.880
thank You,

00:54:29.880 --> 00:54:33.710
Father,

00:54:36.150 --> 00:54:36.160
that

00:54:39.040 --> 00:54:41.069
we

00:54:42.200 --> 00:54:44.430
keep telling people how to

00:54:44.440 --> 00:54:49.030
find Jesus. We love you all. We pray

00:54:49.040 --> 00:54:51.789
covering over President Trump and over

00:54:51.799 --> 00:54:53.510
his cabinet. And

00:54:57.520 --> 00:54:59.109
we thank You, Lord, that Elon Musk is

00:54:59.119 --> 00:55:00.510
born

00:55:00.520 --> 00:55:02.990
again.

00:55:03.000 --> 00:55:06.870
Amen and amen.

00:55:06.880 --> 00:55:09.750
Well, if you're new here and you want to

00:55:09.760 --> 00:55:12.990
subscribe, subscribe. If not, it's cool.

00:55:15.760 --> 00:55:18.950
I'm just tired of

00:55:24.630 --> 00:55:24.640
the

00:55:34.799 --> 00:55:37.470
hoopla.

00:55:37.480 --> 00:55:38.390
It helps the

00:55:38.400 --> 00:55:40.309
algorithm and helps get the

00:55:40.319 --> 00:55:42.430
gospel out, but if you get

00:55:42.440 --> 00:55:43.750
it,

00:55:43.760 --> 00:55:45.390
you get it.

00:56:00.160 --> 00:56:03.430
We love you all and appreciate

00:56:03.440 --> 00:56:05.630
the

00:56:05.640 --> 00:56:08.829
support for my family.

00:56:35.839 --> 00:56:40.910
God bless

00:56:40.920 --> 00:56:43.510
you all. Put a smile on your face and

00:56:43.510 --> 00:56:43.520
a

00:56:43.520 --> 00:56:46.150
song in your heart. Jesus loves you so

00:56:46.160 --> 00:56:49.950
much, and we love you.

00:56:49.960 --> 00:56:51.990
We will see you

00:56:52.000 --> 00:56:57.280
all again soon. God bless you all. Bye-bye.

